      "span_text": "As cisplatin causes nephrotoxicity, it has been suggested that the toxic effects of cisplatin may be related to free radical induced damage which can be reduced by the supplementation of antioxidants  leading to the possibility that cisplatin may be used in combination with antioxidants which might suppress the drug-induced toxic effects."
